  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  IPAH

          -  &gt; 3 months treatment with bosentan

          -  6 minute walk distance 150 - 425 m

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  other forms of pulmonary hypertension

          -  severe comorbidities

          -  cotreatment with sildenafil or investigational drugs
      </textblock>
